You are unaggressive and somewhat dependent.
You are down-to-earth: you prefer facts over fantasy. You are unconcerned with art: you are less concerned with artistic or creative activities than most people who participated in our surveys. And you are proud: you hold yourself in high regard, satisfied with who you are.
